{"tid":765070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣幫男朋友？","createTime":"2018-08-02T12:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T12:56:23.000Z","uid":72339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05974db51a395d93deeaf61e5473e15aeb6f6092","tid":765070,"uid":72339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"如果你男朋友 係對你好好<br />\n同佢相處好舒服<br />\n<br />\n但佢永遠都好似慢你一步<br />\n連佢自己都覺<br />\n<br />\n我係一個好勤力既人<br />\n但佢就比較懶 <br />\n你唔開心佢俾唔到意見你<br />\n甚至好多時要你幫佢解決問題<br />\n<br />\n佢自己都覺自己有問題<br />\n面對問題時只係自卑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我到底可以點幫佢？<br />\n會唔會大家仲係學生所以先咁？ 過多兩年出黎會野佢會唔會變成熟點？☹️"},{"pid":"0462b3a42d80a6d5383e9d4069994dfdb2cb106a","tid":765070,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/205619_949028869db26c771c6d11efc059f7d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F205619_949028869db26c771c6d11efc059f7d3.png&h=973ee85f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}